📊 Sales and Product Analysis Dashboard – Power BI
This Power BI dashboard was developed to provide comprehensive insights into sales performance and product-level analytics.
The objective was to enable data-driven decision-making by visualizing key metrics and trends related to sales, revenue, and product performance
across multiple dimensions such as time, geography, and customer segments.

🔍 Key Features
📈 Sales Overview Dashboard
✅ Total Sales, Revenue, and Profit KPIs
📊 Year-over-Year and Month-over-Month Trends
🌍 Sales Breakdown by Region, Country, and Sales Representatives
📦 Product Performance Analysis
🥇 Top-Selling and Low-Performing Products
📐 Sales Contribution by Product Categories
📉 Product Lifecycle and Trend Patterns
👥 Customer Insights
🧩 Sales by Customer Segments
🔁 Customer Retention and Acquisition Metrics
💵 Average Order Value and Purchase Frequency

🛠 Tools & Technologies
Power BI Desktop
Excel / SQL / SharePoint / OneDrive as data sources
